[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    440[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mFix:[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m Promote the production-gaps content into the architecture pattern. Specify the stratified sampling composition, the cycle cadence, the disagreement-capture data structure, the active-learning feedback loop cadence, and the conflict-of-interest screening.[K
